style=\'color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\'><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\r\n style=\'width:24pt;height:24pt\'>\r\n <v:imagedata croptop=\"-65520f\" cropbottom=\"65520f\"/>\r\n</v:shape><span style=\'mso-element:field-end\'></span></span><![endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 21.6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Who We Are -</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Blood Bank is a comprehensive\r\nonline platform designed to streamline the blood donation process and ensure a\r\nreliable supply of blood for those in need. Our team consists of healthcare\r\nprofessionals, IT experts, and dedicated volunteers who are passionate about\r\nmaking a difference in the world.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 21.6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Our Vision -</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Our vision is to create a world where no one suffers due to a lack of\r\nblood. We aim to bridge the gap between blood donors and recipients through an\r\ninnovative, user-friendly platform that fosters a community of regular donors\r\nand ensures a steady, safe, and adequate blood supply.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 21.6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">What We Do -</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: x-large;\">Donor Registration and Management: We provide an easy registration\r\nprocess for donors, allowing them to create profiles, track their donation\r\nhistory, and receive reminders for their next eligible donation date.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 21.6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;